docs.text: Welcome to DataScIIEnce About Welcome to the DataScIIEnce official GitHub webpage, which centralizes the different projects, sessions materials and snippets useful for Machine Learning and Data Analysis. DataScIIEnce is the Data science, Machine & Deep learning student club of ENSIIE Paris , French engineering school specialized in applied mathematics, high-performance computing and computer science. Follow us GitHub LinkedIn Instagram Website Contact Please use the form available here
